.TH start-cli-tunnel-dns 1  "dns " 
.SH NAME
start\-cli\-tunnel\-dns \- View or edit injected DNS records
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBstart\-cli tunnel dns\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
View or edit injected DNS records
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
start\-cli\-tunnel\-dns\-add(1)
